      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It\u2019s not every day you come across a gem that\u2019s been treated this well. I\u2019ve absolutely adored this car, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve spent countless Saturday mornings making sure every inch is spotless and garage-kept, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets. She drives like a dream\u2014smooth, responsive, and ready for a new adventure. If you're looking for that pristine, 'new car' feeling without the dealership hassle, come by for a chat and a look. I\u2019d love to see her go to someone who appreciates a truly immaculate machine!",
      "price": 48900.0,
