      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level F80 M3, meticulously optimized for the discerning driver. The S55 twin-turbo inline-six delivers surgical precision with a recalibrated torque curve and zero-lag spooling. It features an upgraded active M differential and reinforced subframe bushings to eliminate deflection under heavy cornering loads. Every fluid service has been performed at half-intervals using high-shear synthetics to ensure maximum thermal stability. The DCT shifts are crisp and instantaneous, paired with a chassis that offers unparalleled rigidity and feedback. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically perfected specimen with a flawless service history and factory-plus tolerances.",
